ğŸš€ About The Project

ExamPro is a full-stack web application built to simplify online MCQ-based assessments.

Educators can:

Create timed tests

Schedule activation

Share via unique test codes

Students can:

Enter via test code

Attempt timed assessments

Get instant scoring with detailed breakdown

ğŸ¯ Vision

To provide a lightweight, accessible alternative to complex LMS platforms.

âœ¨ Features
ğŸ” Authentication & Security

6-digit OTP email verification via Gmail SMTP

BCrypt password hashing

Password strength validation

Secure login/logout

Professional branded HTML email templates

ğŸ“ Test Creation (Educators)

Unlimited MCQs

Custom duration in minutes

Scheduled activation (date + time)

Preview mode before publishing

Draft auto-save via LocalStorage

Unique 8-character shareable test codes

Copy test link in one click

âœï¸ Test Taking (Students)

Code-based access

Countdown timer with visual warnings

Previous/Next navigation

Modify answers before submission

Auto-submit on timer expiry

One attempt per student

Question progress indicator

ğŸ“Š Results & Review

Instant scoring

Percentage calculation

Performance rating

Question-by-question breakdown

Green/Red color coding

Student answer vs correct answer comparison

