ğŸ—„ Database Schema
Core Entities

USERS

TESTS

QUESTIONS

TEST_RESULTS

STUDENT_ANSWERS

Relationships

A User creates multiple Tests

A Test contains multiple Questions

A User can attempt multiple Tests

Each TestResult stores student answers

